case.title: Looking for a nice open guy! - 32 (London)
case.text: Hi, I am Kate , I am 32 white working women I have two boys and don't mind if you have children too or not but I do and it's not a problem to me .i work and in joy the gym and camping and music and films and books but don't want to bore you with the normal :). I looking for a guy from 28/34 to take things slow and see where we end up hopefully some where good but who knows ,must be faithful and understanding and funny . Thanks so much for your time Kate .
